snippet.title: NEON KNIGHTS HUMANITY ERASED Gameplay Trailer (TBA) 4K
snippet.description:
Neon Knights: Humanity Erased Official Pre-Alpha Gameplay Trailer New for PC in remastered/upscaled 4K ULTRA HD quality and improved to smooth 60 FPS.

Release date: TBA 2021 or later

Neon Knights: Humanity Erased is a psychological cyber noir. Discover a dark mystery only a digital exorcist possessed by a hacker can solve. Expose disturbing secrets and confront horrific Holos - digital demons born from tragedy and corruption. The game is being developed by Eddaheim.

Devs YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCE4BQ6olYcJwABwwrY3Fbig

Enjoy, like & share for more game news videos!
